titles.title: Designating minority membership to the Committee on the Budget.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 1/26/1993--Introduced. Elects the following Representatives to the House Committee on the Budget: (1) Wally Herger, California, and Jim Bunning, Kentucky, to rank after Olympia J. Snowe, Maine; and (3) David L. Hobson, Ohio, to rank after Wayne Allard, Colorado.
